      <description>YouTube Video Resources SSSD on Ubuntu Server Guide (look for the LDAP section) Video Transcript Once we&amp;rsquo;ve set up and configured our OpenLDAP server on Linux, we can configure another VM to act as an LDAP client and use that server for authentication. Thankfully, now that Ubuntu 20.04 uses SSSD, this process is pretty simple.
