      <description>It appears that I have managed to confuse lots of people with the Windows AD portion of this lab. That&amp;rsquo;s not my intent, and any confusion is totally my fault here. This is mostly due to the fact that I reused an older video showing how to set up an Active Directory server and not clearly describing how things should be changed. I&amp;rsquo;ll do my best to clarify what you need to know and how you can adapt any existing setup you may have so that it works.</description>
